      "author": "NeuroCloud-Activate",
      "description": "Light-LiveSync 0.1.12 adds batched remote apply behavior, an Activity-tab backup recovery tool, and README cleanup for automatic first sync and fast pull/apply behavior.\\n\\nHighlights:\\n- Pulled remote files now apply in batches by default instead of one file at a time.\\n- Advanced settings now expose the maximum remote files applied per sync.\\n- Settings now include a recovery area for restoring files from automatic recovery backups.\\n- README wording now reflects automatic first full-vault sync and removes obsolete build/mobile sections.\\n\\nVerified locally with typecheck, production build, 23 harnesses, package creation, release verification, privacy sweep, and testing-vault install audit.",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "Light-LiveSync 0.1.12",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-06-02T11:48:39Z",
      "tag": "0.1.12"
