      "author": "NeuroCloud-Activate",
      "description": "Light-LiveSync 0.1.11 fixes the manifest description punctuation warning and makes first full-vault sync automatic for setup/startup/periodic sync when the remote has no current vault documents. The sync engine now asks the plugin to scan and queue the current vault after remote inspection confirms an empty vault, then pushes without requiring manual Sync now. Harness evidence includes automaticFirstSyncQueued=true and automaticFirstSyncPulledOwnUpload=false.",
      "draft": false,
