      "author": "NeuroCloud-Activate",
      "description": "Light-LiveSync 0.1.10 adds verified full-vault sync behavior. Manual Sync now recursively scans vault config, hidden files, and other plugin data through the vault adapter while keeping Light-LiveSync's own volatile runtime data and generated preview/staging/conflict folders local-only. Large text files now use larger chunks and CouchDB writes are safely batched to avoid oversized bulk requests. First full-vault uploads to an empty remote skip pulling back the same device's own uploads. Verified against the testing vault using saved plugin credentials: 380 files queued and pushed, 0 failed uploads, 0 conflicts, 0 pending push, 0 pending apply, with the remote ending at 3,083 documents after optimized chunking.",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "Light-LiveSync 0.1.10",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-06-02T04:45:31Z",
