      "author": "NeuroCloud-Activate",
      "description": "Light-LiveSync 0.1.1 focuses on smoother mobile and first-sync behavior.\\n\\nChanges:\\n- Saved sync credentials now restore automatically on app start for the same device.\\n- CouchDB addresses are normalized more carefully, including plain IP/host entries and HTTPS domains.\\n- Default upload batch size is raised for full-vault first syncs while unchanged-file fingerprints still prevent redundant uploads.\\n- Vault configuration and plugin data files can now sync.\\n- Runtime checks run automatically in the background instead of needing manual settings buttons.\\n- Settings are split into Sync, Sync activity, and Advanced pages, with the old safety explanation removed.",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "Light-LiveSync 0.1.1",
      "prerelease": false,
