      "description": "Initial Light-LiveSync release.\\n\\nHighlights:\\n- Simple CouchDB live sync for Obsidian with setup URI compatibility.\\n- E2EE-required sync defaults and encrypted local credential storage.\\n- 60-second edit batching, small sync batches, and offline-aware retry behavior.\\n- Automatic text merge with recovery backups.\\n- Calm status presentation plus runtime checks and non-secret evidence reporting.",
